  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/5891424285e3a7404b49952a305cc0ec.poster.avif?t=1771009915\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/5891424285e3a7404b49952a305cc0ec.webm?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/5891424285e3a7404b49952a305cc0ec.mp4?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Jimmy the Sloth embarks on his own magical adventure. Think Lion Quest, but with a sloth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sloth Tales delights and inspires with the following features:</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/45852e83457443833e9139eb9c36feba.poster.avif?t=1771009915\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/45852e83457443833e9139eb9c36feba.webm?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/45852e83457443833e9139eb9c36feba.mp4?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A mighty-fine and very free platforming adventure. Where you play as Jimmy the Sloth.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/87959740d7ed5b98264d891027f5b758.poster.avif?t=1771009915\" width=1170 height=652 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/87959740d7ed5b98264d891027f5b758.webm?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/87959740d7ed5b98264d891027f5b758.mp4?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dash and high-jump powerups redefine play with new ways to explore.<br></li><li>A light amount of story – just enough to leave you wanting more!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/760c243446db08d6b8c562e35d1e0da8.poster.avif?t=1771009915\" width=1170 height=652 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/760c243446db08d6b8c562e35d1e0da8.webm?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/760c243446db08d6b8c562e35d1e0da8.mp4?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Open-ended design where the levels can be played through in any order. Plus a small amount of randomness ensures no two Sloth Tales are exactly the same.<br></li><li>Soundtrack is a brand-new song by the band Falcon Ave. – perhaps their catchiest one yet.</li></ul><br>––––<br><br>Approx. playtime 30 mins (maybe 1hr if you take your time)<br><br><br>Sloth Tales is a standalone adventure, but it's also part of the even-more amazing game Lion Quest Infinity, which is also available on Steam.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/5891424285e3a7404b49952a305cc0ec.poster.avif?t=1771009915\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/5891424285e3a7404b49952a305cc0ec.webm?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/5891424285e3a7404b49952a305cc0ec.mp4?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Jimmy the Sloth embarks on his own magical adventure. Think Lion Quest, but with a sloth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sloth Tales delights and inspires with the following features:</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/45852e83457443833e9139eb9c36feba.poster.avif?t=1771009915\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/45852e83457443833e9139eb9c36feba.webm?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/45852e83457443833e9139eb9c36feba.mp4?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A mighty-fine and very free platforming adventure. Where you play as Jimmy the Sloth.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/87959740d7ed5b98264d891027f5b758.poster.avif?t=1771009915\" width=1170 height=652 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/87959740d7ed5b98264d891027f5b758.webm?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/87959740d7ed5b98264d891027f5b758.mp4?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dash and high-jump powerups redefine play with new ways to explore.<br></li><li>A light amount of story – just enough to leave you wanting more!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/760c243446db08d6b8c562e35d1e0da8.poster.avif?t=1771009915\" width=1170 height=652 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/760c243446db08d6b8c562e35d1e0da8.webm?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/760c243446db08d6b8c562e35d1e0da8.mp4?t=1771009915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Open-ended design where the levels can be played through in any order. Plus a small amount of randomness ensures no two Sloth Tales are exactly the same.<br></li><li>Soundtrack is a brand-new song by the band Falcon Ave. – perhaps their catchiest one yet.</li></ul><br>––––<br><br>Approx. playtime 30 mins (maybe 1hr if you take your time)<br><br><br>Sloth Tales is a standalone adventure, but it's also part of the even-more amazing game Lion Quest Infinity, which is also available on Steam.",
